data.title: Rome2Rio
data.meta_description: Rome2Rio is an Australian online multimodal transport journey planner offering travel services globally. The company is based in Melbourne, Australia, and is owned by the German online travel comparison and booking website Omio.
data.text:
Rome2Rio is an Australian online multimodal transport journey planner offering travel services globally.[1] The company is based in Melbourne, Australia, and is owned by the German online travel comparison and booking website Omio.
